room_title: Escape room "Boardwalk Meyham" by Room For Escape in Atlantic City
room_address: 112 Woodland Ave Suite 202 Somers Point, NJ 08244
room_description: Artic Diamond Heist but it has melted away and has come back as Boardwalk Mayhem. Your cat Mr. Riddleworth has gotten into the candy locker at the boardwalk and eaten so much candy he cannot get out the way he has gotten in. You must help him escape before the owner shows up.
